    "instanceId": "day9-linkedin-challenge",
    "notes": "SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:\n1. Replace YOUR_GOOGLE_SHEET_ID with your actual Google Sheet ID\n2. Connect your OpenAI, Gmail, Google Sheets, and (optional) Slack credentials\n3. POST to the webhook URL with this body:\n{\n  'leads': [\n    {\n      'name': 'Jane Smith',\n      'email': 'jane@company.com',\n      'role': 'Head of Operations',\n      'company': 'Acme Corp',\n      'industry': 'SaaS',\n      'bio': 'Passionate about scaling ops with smart tooling',\n      'pain_point': 'manual reporting and tool fragmentation',\n      'linkedin_url': 'https://linkedin.com/in/janesmith'\n    }\n  ],\n  'sender_name': 'Your Name',\n  'sender_role': 'AI Automation Expert',\n  'your_offer': 'n8n workflows that eliminate 10+ hours of manual work per week',\n  'mode': 'draft'\n}\n4. Set mode to 'send' to send directly, or 'draft' to save to Gmail drafts\n5. Check Google Sheets 'Leads' tab for the full log of generated emails"
